  "remarks": "TAi.044 Title: Maulavi. Designation: a) Minister of Higher Education under the Taliban regime, b) Mayor of Kabul City under the Taliban regime. Member of the Taliban Supreme Council. Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 23 Jul. 2010.; Listing: Listed by UN 1267 Committee on 23 February 2001 (amended on 21 Sep 2007, 3 Oct. 2008, 29 Nov. 2011)",
